metadata.name: small islands
metadata.description:
This collection of paintings in inspired by nature.
in the machine world,despite the high stress, creating imaginary images of nature is a good way for me to deal whith stress.
i love tress and small islands and i always try to paint them as i imagine them in my meind.
There is also physical version of this painting 
Acrylic on canvas 
Size:100*70
